    <node id="Boston Celtics">
      <data key="d0">Boston Celtics</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">The Boston Celtics is a professional basketball team in the NBA, commonly referred to as the Celtics.&lt;SEP&gt;The Boston Celtics is a professional basketball team that won the game by 20 points.&lt;SEP&gt;The Boston Celtics is a professional basketball team based in Boston, Massachusetts.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-32a578207f6d74c1c5525025cedd5c54&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-51c3da8183fc6567f29832f7f1f818ab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83490cf4307195fbb6dc1b0d1db14c37</data>
